ce even if a small set of protein pairs is\nprovided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2009 17:56:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Nov 2010 11:52:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2013 06:50:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-30"}
