ial $p$ as above, the associated Garding cone is a monotonicity\ncone for all branches of the the equation p(Hess u) = 0 where Hess u denotes\nthe riemannian Hessian of u.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Dec 2009 15:46:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Mar 2010 15:45:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-03-22"}
